&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>Instinct is something which every life has on this planet. &lt;br>
And it helps them in their survival. &lt;br>
If survival is the goal of life then instinct is good enough.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>But human has two other great capabilities &lt;br>
which other animals don&amp;rsquo;t have. &lt;br>
These are the capabilities of reasoning and intuition.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>